c_j:= j\cdot\mu\{|X_0-\mathbb E(X_0)|\geqslant kj\}.
\sum_{n=1}^\infty c_n=\sum_{n=1}^\infty n\sum_{j\geqslant n}\mu(A_j)\leqslant \sum_j j^2\mu(A_j)\leqslant \frac 1{k^2}\sum_j\int_{A_j}|X_0-\mathbb E(X_0)|^2\mathrm d\mu=\frac1{k^2}\operatorname{Var}(X_0).
